Architecture-specific notes
---------------------------

  * `eqt_rose/eqt_rose.pt` — EQTransformer fine-tuned from the INSTANCE
    pretrained weights. Cite Mousavi et al. (2020) for the architecture.

  * `phasenet_rose/phasenet_rose.pt` — PhaseNet fine-tuned from the
    INSTANCE pretrained weights. Cite Zhu & Beroza (2019) for the
    architecture.

  * `redpan_tf60/train.hdf5` — RED-PAN MTAN R2U-Net retrained on
    Taiwan + STEAD + INSTANCE + RoSE, warm-started from the published
    RED-PAN(60s) weights. Cite Liao et al. (2022) for the architecture
    and the original RED-PAN training recipe.

The integrity of each file can be verified against `SHA256SUMS`.
